partman-auto (61) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Martin Michlmayr ]
  * Increase the minimimum amount of swap created from 64 to 96 MB.  This
    is needed for installations on systems with 32 MB RAM and only a 1 GB
    drive.  Closes: #399951.

