partman-auto (54ubuntu4) edgy; urgency=low

  * Use expr rather than shell arithmetic in resize_use_free, since dash
    doesn't support 64-bit arithmetic.
  * Change backup exit code from automatically_partition do_option scripts
    from 254 to 99, to match similar changes in Debian.
  * Support backup from partman-partitioning/impossible_resize errors in
    resize_use_free.

 -- Colin Watson <cjwatson@ubuntu.com>  Thu, 21 Sep 2006 11:26:08 +0100

